relevant_findings.general: Chronically ill appearing woman in NAD, appears older than stated age.
relevant_findings.eyes: Extra-occular movements intact, pupils equal round, reactive to light, sclera anicteric, not injected, no exudates.
relevant_findings.ENT: Mucus membranes moist, no ulcerations or exudates.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1, S2, no murmurs, rubs or gallops.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales or rhonchi.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, non tender, non distended, no hepatosplenomegaly, bowel sounds present, no fluid wave.
relevant_findings.extremities: No cyanosis, clubbing, edema, joint swelling.
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented x3, CN II-XII intact, normal attention, sensation normal, asterixis absent, speech fluent, DTRs 2+ bilaterally.
relevant_findings.integument: Warm, moist, no rash or ulceration.
